commit.message: break it down into model classes
sketch out the regression model training cycle
add a draft schema to support snapshots and multiple training runs for a project
use bytea directly for pl/python rather than hex/text conversion
keep model in memory to avoid going to disk
remove validate because validation has a different meaning in ML, and we will be more liberal with data types we accept
Use unittest as the test running harness
